title: RP
body: I tried to buy the 20$ RP but i accidently entered the expiration date wrong, my mom got a message on her phone saying that i did pay for the RP but i didnt get anything. Please help

replies.body: We'd like to help!  Reach out to us in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so our billing team can take a look and see what's going on.  We'll respond asap!
